Class PropertyMaps.NavigationAttributes

java.lang.Object
com.here.platform.location.integration.optimizedmap.graph.javadsl.PropertyMaps.NavigationAttributes
Enclosing class:
PropertyMaps
public static final class PropertyMaps.NavigationAttributes extends Object
Provides factory methods for accessing properties from the navigationattributes layer of Optimized Map for Location Library.
